summary:
I'm passionate about products that have a positive impact on the world. My work revolves around translating designs and ideas into implementations with performance in mind. While I think products shouldn't be judged solely on their face value - a great user experience is one factor that compels users return to a product, and this is where my expertise lies.

React and React Native are my tools of choice when it comes to implementing Web and Mobile applications. And I'm well versed in NodeJS and .NET Core for server side implementations.
